            {
              "content": "# Customer Onboarding\n\n> Automatically processes new customer registrations and notifies the sales team.\n\n| Property | Value |\n|----------|-------|\n| Status | ✅ Active |\n| Trigger | Webhook |\n| Last Sync | 2026-07-15 |\n| GitSync Version | v1.0 |\n\n\n# {{ Workflow Name }}\n\n> {{ One sentence describing what this workflow does. }}\n\n---\n\n## 📌 Overview\n\n{{ 2–4 sentence overview }}\n\nExplain what this workflow automates, why it exists, and what outcome it produces.\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Purpose\n\n{{ Business purpose }}\n\nExample:\n\nThis workflow automates the customer onboarding process by validating incoming requests, creating customer records, notifying internal teams, and sending confirmation emails.\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ Trigger\n\n| Type | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| Webhook | Receives customer registration requests |\n\nExamples:\n\n- Manual Trigger\n- Webhook\n- Schedule\n- Slack Event\n- Form Submission\n- Email Trigger\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 Workflow Summary\n\n```text\nWebhook\n    │\nValidate Request\n    │\nCreate Customer\n    │\nGenerate Invoice\n    │\nSend Welcome Email\n    │\nNotify Slack\n```\n\nA simple high-level flow.\n\nNot every node.\n\n---\n\n## 🔌 Integrations\n\nThis workflow communicates with:\n\n| Service | Purpose |\n|----------|----------|\n| Slack | Team notifications |\n| OpenAI | AI processing |\n| Google Sheets | Store customer data |\n| Gmail | Send emails |\n\nOnly include detected integrations.\n\n---\n\n## 📥 Inputs\n\nWhat starts this workflow?\n\nExample\n\n- Webhook payload\n- Google Form\n- Slack command\n- Cron schedule\n\n---\n\n## 📤 Outputs\n\nWhat does this workflow produce?\n\nExamples\n\n- Customer created\n- Email sent\n- Google Sheet updated\n- Slack notification delivered\n\n---\n\n## ⚙️ Requirements\n\nThis workflow requires:\n\n- Slack credentials\n- OpenAI credentials\n- Gmail account\n\nOnly include requirements detected from the workflow.\n\nNever invent credentials.\n\n---\n\n## 🏷 Tags\n\n- AI\n- Sales\n- Learning\n- Automation\n\n---\n\n## 📝 Notes\n\nAnything important another developer should know.\n\nExamples\n\n- Uses environment variables\n- Webhook must be registered\n- Requires external API access\n\nIf nothing important is detected:\n\n> No special requirements detected.\n\n---\n\n## 📂 Repository Files\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `{{ Workflow Name }}.json` | Workflow definition managed automatically by GitSync |\n| `README.md` | Documentation generated by AI and editable by you |\n\n---\n\n## 🤖 Generated by GitSync for n8n\n\nThis README was generated automatically by GitSync for n8n.\n\nYou are free to edit this file manually.\n\nFuture AI-generated updates will require your approval before replacing this documentation.",
